*uuidtools-1.0.5 (01 Dec 2008)

  01 Dec 2008; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +uuidtools-1.0.5.ebuild:
  Version bump; use tarball rather than gem: the installed package is
  smaller, it has no rake/rspec dependencies, and tests are executed with
  FEATURES=test.

  03 Nov 2008; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> uuidtools-1.0.4.ebuild:
